<div style="text-align: center; width: 100%;">
	<h2>Welcome to MyDaddyPuzzles.com</h2>
</div>

<p style="line-height: 1.25em;"><span class="first_letter">T</span>hank you for visiting MyDaddyPuzzles.com, where you'll find high quality, hand-crafted, durable puzzles that will thrill your children and grandchildren for years to come.  Our puzzles are created in our home and tested by our young sons (ages four and eighteen months). They are made out of solid poplar and are stained and sealed or painted with <a href="http://www.cpsc.gov/cpscpub/pubs/5016.html" target="_blank">ASTM D-4236 Compliant</a> stains. We use stains and paints that are non-toxic and are tested and approved by the <a href="http://www.cpsc.gov" target="_blank">Consumer Product Safety Commmision</a>. Our puzzles are beautifully-made and are just as fun to display as they are to play with.</p>

