<p><%= image_tag 'a_show_of_hands.jpg', :style => 'float: left;margin-right: 30px;margin-bottom: 40px;', :title => "A Show of Hands Logo" %><span class="first_letter">W</span>e are proud to announce that MyDaddyPuzzles will now be available for purchase in the historic Del Ray neighborhood of Alexandria at <a href="http://www.ashowofhands.biz" target="_blank">A Show of Hands</a>.</p>
<p>A Show of Hands will offer up 23 of our puzzle designs for sale among their other wonderful locally made items.  We are very pleased to have our work showcased this popular Alexandria shop located on Mount Vernon Avenue.  To see hours of operation visit their website at <a href="http://www.ashowofhands.biz" target="_blank">www.ashowofhands.biz</a>. </p>

